headline: Arizona Utilities Plan to Join Markets+ to Strengthen Grid Reliability and Resilience
summary: PHOENIX & TUCSON, Ariz., November 25, 2024--Arizona Public Service, Salt River Project, Tucson Electric Power and UniSource plan to join Southwest Power Pool's Markets+ to benefit customers.
